              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Head of AI Division</h4>
              <p class="text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-400 font-medium">Extracurricular Organization</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 italic mb-4">2023 - 2024 | Jakarta</p>
