                <li>Led and organized the AI Division within the extracurricular organization</li>
                <li>Taught basic AI concepts and AI logic implementation using Python</li>
                <li>Guided members in applying AI in computer vision, automation, and basic language processing</li>
                <li>Developed AI-based projects to enhance members' understanding and skills in AI technology</li>
              </ul>
        </div>

            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-4 border-secondary-500 dark:border-secondary-400 py-4 glass-card rounded-r-xl p-6">
              <div class="absolute -left-3 top-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-secondary-500 shadow-lg shadow-secondary-500/30"></div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Member of Commission B</h4>
              <p class="text-secondary-600 dark:text-secondary-400 font-medium">Student Council (OSIS)</p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 italic mb-4">2022 - 2023 | Jakarta</p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                <li>Equipped with teamwork skills and good communication methods for managing and supervising OSIS members</li>
                <li>Served in this position for one term</li>
              </ul>
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Education & Achievements -->
        <div class="opacity-0" data-scroll data-animate="fade-in-up" style="--delay: 300ms;">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-gradient inline-block">Education & Achievements</h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-4 border-accent-500 dark:border-accent-400 py-4 glass-card rounded-r-xl p-6">
              <div class="absolute -left-3 top-5 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent-500 shadow-lg shadow-accent-500/30"></div>
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Software Engineering</h4>
